   "source": [
    "# 🌤️ AireCare — Weather & Health Risk Prediction\n",
    "\n",
    "**What this does:**  \n",
    "Looks at daily weather in India and predicts if today is a high-risk day for:\n",
    "- 🤕 Migraine\n",
    "- 🤧 Allergy\n",
    "- 🦴 Joint Pain\n",
    "\n",
    "**How the app would work:**  \n",
    "User says which conditions they have → app checks today's weather → sends a risk alert\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
