    "### Chart 3 — Correlation heatmap\n",
    "Which weather features are most related to each condition?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "fd3d1cc8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
